20husband%20and%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20until%20about%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20we%20rarely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-is-bahama-breeze-worth-it-for-family-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eate%20at%20chain%20restaurants%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20with%20rising%20food%20costs%20and%20our%20two%20teens%20wanting%20to%20check%20out%20the%20chains%20and%20dishes%20they%20keep%20seeing%20on%20social%20media%2C%20we've%20started%20to%20lean%20in.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20love%20getting%20breakfast%20together%20on%20the%20weekends%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20visit%20Bob%20Evans%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20see%20what%20kind%20of%20value%20we'd%20find.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20our%20visit%20to%20the%20famous%20chain%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBob%20Evans%20has%20reinvented%20itself%20a%20few%20times%20in%20recent%20decades.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bob%20Evans%20exterior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cb4abc992e8c7f195%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBob%20Evans%20has%20been%20around%20for%20decades.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20casual-dining%20chain%20Bob%20Evans%20is%20known%20for%20its%20country%20vibes%2C%20sausages%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bfarm-fresh%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrying-eating-breakfast-every-day-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall-day%20breakfast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lunch%2C%20and%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20with%20Robert%20%26quot%3BBob%26quot%3B%20Evans%20opening%20the%20restaurant%20that'd%20later%20become%20Bob%20Evans%20in%20Ohio%20in%201962.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20company%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbob-evans-cfo-explains-turnaround-plans-2015-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereinvented%20itself%20a%20few%20times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20sold%20to%20a%20private-equity%20firm%20in%202017%20for%20%24565%20million%2C%20and%20was%20exploring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2022-01-10%2Fbob-evans-restaurants-is-said-to-explore-600-million-sale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esale%20at%20a%20%24600%20million%20valuation%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20March%2C%20Axios%20reported%20that%20Bob%20Evans%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2Fpro%2Fretail-deals%2F2024%2F03%2F27%2Fbob-evans-retains-investment-bank-kroll-sale-auction-restaurant-private-equity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20with%20the%20investment%20bank%20Kroll%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20the%20company%20could%20be%20back%20on%20the%20market%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restaurantbusinessonline.com%2Ffinancing%2Fbob-evans-puts-itself-market%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseeking%20a%20buyer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20writing%2C%20the%20chain%20has%20about%20500%20locations%20in%2018%20US%20states.%20We%20visited%20one%20in%20Florida.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20started%20our%20breakfast%20with%20drinks.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drink%20on%20Bob%20Evans%20table%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cb4abc992e8c7f194%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20a%20seasonal%20drink%20with%20my%20breakfast.%20%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20Bob%20Evans%20menu%20has%20just%20about%20everything%3A%20mimosas%2C%20pancakes%2C%20omelets%2C%20burgers%2C%20soup-and-salad%20combos%2C%20and%20more.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%2C%20my%20son%20and%20I%20ordered%20a%20mixed%20juice%20drink%20off%20of%20the%20seasonal%20menu.%20Our%20drinks%20were%20%244%20each%20and%20pretty%20tasty%2C%20if%20not%20a%20little%20sugary.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20got%20a%20flavored%20iced%20tea%20(%243.50)%20and%20my%20husband%20ordered%20a%20classic%20cup%20of%20coffee%20(%243).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20breakfast%20appetizer%20was%20a%20little%20underwhelming.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plate%20of%20bacon%20at%20Bob%20Evans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cf27898f532d60f79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20order%20of%20bacon%20came%20with%20five%20pieces.%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20that%20Bob%20Evans%20serves%20breakfast%20appetizers%2C%20and%20we%20were%20powerless%20to%20resist%20the%20Blue%20Ribbon%20Bacon%2C%20center-cut%2C%20hardwood-smoked%20bacon%20glazed%20with%20black-pepper-maple%20honey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%245%20order%20of%20bacon%20came%20with%20five%20honey-glazed%20strips%20that%20were%20flavorful%2C%20but%20a%20bit%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I've%20ordered%20specialty%20bacon%20at%20other%20restaurants%20the%20strips%20were%20usually%20thick%20and%20hearty.%20These%20felt%20no%20different%20than%20the%20bacon%20that%20later%20came%20with%20my%20kids'%20breakfasts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBob%20Evans%20had%20a%20great%20value%20menu%2C%20so%20I%20ordered%20from%20that.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sausage%20biscuit%20at%20Bob%20Evans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cf27898f532d60f7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20got%20the%20country-biscuit%20breakfast%20at%20Bob%20Evans.%20%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20often%20find%20chain-restaurant%20portions%20to%20be%20way%20too%20large%2C%20so%20I%20loved%20seeing%20Bob%20Evans'%20%26quot%3Bsunrise%20savers%26quot%3B%20menu%2C%20which%20offered%20smaller%20portions%20of%20breakfast%20fare%2C%20like%20sausage%20gravy%20and%20biscuits%20or%20brioche%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquick-french-toast-everyone-should-know-how-to-make-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrench%20toast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20at%20a%20lower%20price.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20a%20%247%20country-biscuit%20breakfast%3A%20a%20biscuit%20topped%20with%20a%20cooked-to-order%20egg%2C%20sausage%2C%20country%20gravy%2C%20and%20cheddar%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fina-garten-easy-breakfast-potatoes-recipe-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreakfast%20potatoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20my%20favorite%20morning%20treat%2C%20so%20I%20chose%20hash%20browns%20as%20my%20side%20dish.%20Sadly%2C%20the%20hash%20browns%20(both%20on%20my%20plate%20and%20my%20husband's)%20seemed%20undercooked%20%E2%80%94%20each%20bite%20of%20potato%20had%20an%20unpleasantly%20hard%2C%20kind%20of%20raw%20crunch%20to%20it.%20Maybe%20we%20just%20got%20unlucky%20with%20a%20batch%20that%20wasn't%20fried%20long%20enough%20in%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20disappointed%20I%20couldn't%20enjoy%20my%20hash%20browns%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20meal%20was%20tasty.%20I%20had%20a%20ton%20of%20leftovers%20even%20though%20I%20ordered%20a%20value%20portion%20and%20left%20my%20potatoes%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20husband%20ordered%20a%20value-sized%20sampler%20of%20some%20of%20Bob%20Evans'%20classic%20offerings%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Breakfast%20samplers%20at%20Bob%20Evans%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cf27898f532d60f7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20husband%20ordered%20from%20Bob%20Evans'%20value%20menu.%20%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20also%20ordered%20from%20the%20value%20menu.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20chose%20the%20mini%20sampler%2C%20which%20included%20an%20egg%2C%20hash%20browns%2C%20a%20sausage%20patty%2C%20and%20a%20biscuit%20for%20%246.%20He%20also%20added%20a%20side%20order%20of%20sausage%20gravy%20for%20his%20biscuit%20for%20an%20extra%20%242.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20he%20enjoyed%20his%20meal%2C%20minus%20the%20seemingly%20undercooked%20hash%20browns.%20The%20portion%20size%20was%20still%20large%20enough%20that%20he%20took%20some%20home%20and%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20unsurprising%20because%20Bob%20Evans%20is%20known%20for%20its%20sausage%20%E2%80%94%20the%20sausage%20patty%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20his%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20daughter%20loved%20her%20blueberry%20pancakes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blueberry%20pancakes%20at%20Bob%20Evans%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2a8cf27898f532d60f78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20daughter%20said%20Bob%20Evans%20had%20some%20of%20the%20best%20pancakes%20she's%20had%20from%20a%20chain%20restaurant.%20%3Cp%3ETerri%20Peters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20teenage%20daughter%20ordered%20a%20stack%20of%20Bob%20Evans'%20double-blueberry%20hotcakes%2C%20which%20were%20smothered%20in%20blueberry%20topping%2C%20then%20topped%20with%20whipped%20cream%20and%20powdered%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2410%20dish%20came%20with%20a%20side%20of%20breakfast%20meat%20%E2%80%94%20she%20chose%20bacon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20presented%20beautifully.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20really%20enjoyed%20her%20meal%20and%20said%20these%20were%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcracker-barrel-vs-ihop-which-has-better-pancakes-review-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavorite%20chain-restaurant%20pancakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20date.%20She%20ended%20up%20bringing%20more%20than%20half%20of%20this%20gi