tion%20results%20(though%20plenty%20of%20other%20bipartisan%20groups%20and%20PACs%20do%20the%20same%20thing).%20Furthermore%2C%20AIPAC's%20%26quot%3BUnited%20Democracy%20Project%26quot%3B%20super%20PAC%20is%20sustained%20in%20large%20part%20by%20multimillion-dollar%20contributions%20from%20Republican%20megadonors%2C%20even%20as%20the%20PAC%20spends%20mostly%20in%20Democratic%20primaries%20%E2%80%94%20most%20often%20against%20non-white%20progressive%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20megadonors%20who%20prop%20up%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20MAGA%20movement%20to%20attack%20and%20defeat%20a%20handful%20of%20Black%20and%20brown%20progressive%20incumbents%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Democrats%20spokesman%20Usamah%20Adrabi%20told%20me%20of%20AIPAC%2C%20deriding%20Latimer%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bempty%20suit%20that%20is%20just%20a%20vessel%20for%20Republican%20billionaires%20to%20attack%20and%20malign%20Jamaal%20Bowman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20Latimer's%20contributions%20have%20been%20routed%20through%20AIPAC%2C%20and%20a%20Working%20Families%20Party%20analysis%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider%20shows%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20have%20flowed%20to%20the%20county%20executive's%20congressional%20campaign%20from%20donors%20who%20have%20given%20mostly%20to%20Republicans%2C%20including%20Donald%20Trump.%20Latimer%20told%20me%20that%20he's%20%26quot%3Balways%20gotten%20support%20from%20Republican%20people%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20his%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20things%20done%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20elected%20official.%20%26quot%3BThose%20donors%20have%20donated%20to%20me%20primarily%20because%20of%20my%20position%20on%20Israel%2C%20not%20because%20I'm%20pro-choice%20or%20pro-LGBTQ%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAIPAC%20is%20not%20a%20racist%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Latimer%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20say%20that%2C%20'Oh%2C%20it%20goes%20after%20Black%20individuals.'%20Well%2C%20it%20goes%20after%20Squad%20members%2C%20not%20because%20they're%20Black%2C%20but%20because%20they've%20been%20anti-Israel%20in%20their%20various%20positions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatimer%20has%20reported%20raising%20%243.6%20million%20since%20he%20launched%20his%20campaign%2C%20while%20Bowman%20has%20raised%20%242.7%20million%20since%20January%202023.%20The%20county%20executive%20also%20boasts%20far%20more%20local%20financial%20support%3A%20Roughly%2070%25%20of%20Latimer's%20itemized%20contributions%20come%20from%20donors%20in%20New%20York%20state%2C%20and%20roughly%20half%20of%20them%20are%20from%20the%20district.%20Meanwhile%2C%20just%2028.5%25%20of%20Bowman's%20itemized%20contributions%20come%20from%20New%20York%20and%20just%2010%25%20come%20from%20the%20district%2C%20while%20a%20plurality%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%2031%25%20%E2%80%94%20come%20from%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20raising%20%5Bmoney%5D%20from%20interests%20outside%20the%20district%20that%20are%20clearly%20not%20local%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Latimer.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20getting%20it%20from%20people%20who%20are%20local%2C%20who%20don't%20like%20him%2C%20and%20want%20me%20as%20an%20alternative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bebd37a6-3045-4989-ace9-d5f3330ee839%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'They're%20not%20against%20me%20just%20because%20of%20my%20policies%20on%20Israel'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20what's%20made%20the%20race%20so%20contentious%20is%20the%20geography%20of%20the%20district%2C%20which%20spans%20predominantly-Black%20communities%20in%20the%20Bronx%20and%20Mount%20Vernon%2C%20to%20more%20Latino%20and%20mixed%20cities%20like%20Yonkers%20and%20New%20Rochelle%2C%20to%20predominantly%20white%20and%20heavily%20Jewish%20townships%20like%20Scarsdale%2C%20Rye%2C%20and%20Harrison.%20Both%20men%20have%20accused%20the%20other%20of%20not%20representing%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20district%2C%20and%20both%20of%20them%20may%20have%20a%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20district%20represents%20the%20country%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bowman%2C%20who%20has%20long%20lived%20in%20the%20Bronx.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20diverse%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20segregated%20as%20hell.%26quot%3B%20The%20congressman%20speaks%20somewhat%20dismissively%20of%20the%20wealthier%20parts%20of%20the%20district%20that%20lie%20deeper%20into%20Westchester.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20not%20against%20me%20just%20because%20of%20my%20policies%20on%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bowman.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20also%20pro-worker%20over%20corporations%2C%20I%20have%20bills%20that's%20about%20taxing%20the%20wealthy%20and%20making%20sure%20corporations%20pay%20their%20fair%20share.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20travel%20into%20Scarsdale%20and%20Harrison%20and%20get%20to%20know%20the%20people%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Latimer%20said%20of%20Bowman.%20%26quot%3BHe%20focused%20on%20a%20few%20communities%20that%20he%20felt%20he%20could%20connect%20to%2C%20and%20he%20has%20his%20relationships%20there%2C%20and%20he%20ignored%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20district.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELatimer%20has%20his%20own%20challenges%2C%20largely%20stemming%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20he's%20a%20white%20man%20seeking%20to%20unseat%20a%20Black%20incumbent%20in%20a%20majority-minority%20district.%20Though%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20Mount%20Vernon%2C%20Latimer%20has%20long%20lived%20in%20Rye%2C%20and%20the%20core%20of%20his%20support%20lies%20in%20the%20district's%20more%20affluent%20communities.%20%26quot%3BI%20freely%20admit%20that%20in%20the%20Bronx%2C%20I'm%20going%20from%20zero%20to%20somewhere%2C%20because%20I%20haven't%20represented%20the%20Bronx%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Latimer.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20it's%20a%20learning%20curve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rep.%20Jamaal%20Bowman%20speaks%20to%20students%20at%20a%20high%20school%20in%20Mount%20Vernon%2C%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663d16dd9686a6f37bfdf6b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBowman%20addresses%20students%20at%20a%20high%20school%20in%20Mount%20Vernon%2C%20New%20York.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Metzger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20county%20executive%20insists%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Bbaloney%26quot%3B%20to%20say%20that%20he%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20represents%20the%20wealthy%20parts%20of%20the%20district%2C%20ticking%20off%20the%20endorsements%20he's%20garnered%20from%20Democratic%20committees%20in%20majority-minority%20communities%2C%20his%20support%20from%20a%20local%20bus%20drivers'%20union%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Bthese%20are%20people%20who%20live%20in%20urban%20settings%2C%20and%20the%20way%20that%20I've%20worked%20with%20them%20and%20dealt%20with%20them%20is%20absolutely%20positive%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20his%20work%20on%20a%20Black%20maternal%20health%20initiative%2C%20and%20the%20work%20that%20his%20county%20government%20did%20to%20repair%20Memorial%20Field%2C%20a%20stadium%20that's%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20used%20by%20young%20people%20and%20African%20American%20young%20people%20in%20Mount%20Vernon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20Mount%20Vernon%20High%20School%20where%20Bowman%20%E2%80%94%20a%20longtime%20educator%20who%20founded%20a%20middle%20school%20in%20the%20Bronx%20in%202009%20%E2%80%94%20seemed%20especially%20in%20his%20element.%20Striding%20through%20the%20halls%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20auditorium%2C%20he%20remarked%20that%20the%20school%20%26quot%3Bused%20to%20be%20off%20the%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20a%20new%20principal%20had%20%26quot%3Breally%20turned%20it%20around%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20years.%20As%20he%20addressed%20a%20room%20full%20of%20predominantly-Black%20students%20at%20a%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B-esque%20career%20education%20competition%2C%20he%20held%20up%20his%20iPhone%20