0my%20time%20there%2C%20I%20noticed%20several%20differences%20between%20raising%20a%20family%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20and%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c57b599-fe19-43b4-959e-3016aac98381%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20a%20postpartum%20doula%20covered%20by%20insurance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20nervous%20about%20moving%2C%20I%20was%20told%20I%20couldn't%20have%20picked%20a%20better%20country%20to%20have%20a%20baby%20in%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20Netherlands%20is%20particularly%20amazing%20regarding%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fhow-much-does-childbirth-cost%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echildbirth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20elected%20to%20do%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-home-births-planned-unplanned-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehome%20birth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20could%20not%20have%20had%20a%20better%20experience.%20There%20was%20so%20much%20support%20wrapped%20around%20me.%20A%20midwife%20and%20a%20doula%20were%20with%20me%20through%20the%20birth%2C%20and%20then%20once%20the%20baby%20was%20born%2C%20I%20had%20a%20postpartum%20doula%20come%20to%20the%20house%20for%20eight%20days.%20It%20was%20like%20having%20a%20mother%20care%20for%20me%20without%20any%20of%20the%20baggage%20of%20family%20dynamics.%20She%20just%20cared%20for%20me%20and%20my%20household%2C%20even%20vacuuming%20the%20floors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20care%20was%20paid%20for%20through%20my%20husband's%20insurance.%20It%20would%20be%20the%20same%20care%20received%20by%20any%20working%20family%20because%20every%20person%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20with%20an%20employment%20contract%20is%20entitled%20to%20certain%20statutory%20benefits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20my%20first%20son%20in%20America%2C%20I%20was%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%2048%20hours%2C%20shown%20how%20to%20breastfeed%20and%20diaper%20a%20baby%2C%20and%20then%20sent%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2213aa5f69-e70d-43dd-a3f3-79aa5898c80e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20want%20to%20look%20after%20kids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20our%20first%20excursion%20out%20as%20a%20family%20after%20having%20our%20second%20son%2C%20we%20went%20to%20a%20restaurant%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenihana-experience-is-disapointing-but-revealing-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecommunal%20tables%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20struggling%20with%20the%20baby%2C%20trying%20to%20have%20a%20coffee%2C%20and%20entertaining%20our%207-year-old.%20There%20was%20this%20couple%20who%20had%20finished%20their%20meal%2C%20and%20the%20woman%20said%20she%20would%20hold%20the%20baby%20for%20me.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20it%20would%20be%20weird%20for%20someone%20to%20offer%20that%2C%20and%20even%20weird%20to%20accept%20it.%20But%20it%20was%20our%20first%20taste%20of%20the%20Netherlands'%20culture%20of%20parenting%20as%20a%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20double-checked%20she%20was%20OK%20to%20hold%20the%20baby%20and%20she%20said%20she%20would%20just%20hand%20him%20back%20when%20he%20started%20crying.%20For%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20ate%20my%20meal%20in%20peace.%20It%20was%20amazing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20playgrounds%2C%20parents%20look%20out%20for%20their%20own%20children%20but%20also%20children%20who%20aren't%20theirs.%20If%20a%20child%20is%20being%20rough%2C%20a%20parent%20can%20engage%20to%20tell%20the%20child%20off%20or%20direct%20their%20own%20child%20to%20stand%20up%20for%20themselves.%20The%20US%20isn't%20like%20this%20at%20all.%20Most%20parents%20would%20say%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20parent%20my%20child%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20tell%20me%20how%20to%20parent%20my%20child%26quot%3B.%20But%20not%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246182e7e-4d40-47a7-9f91-ca6e54041ec3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20have%20freedom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%20older%20son%20was%20in%20the%20equivalent%20of%20second%20grade%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20he%20started%20biking%20to%20school%20by%20himself.%20Other%20kids%20were%20doing%20the%20same%2C%20so%20we%20felt%20secure%20to%20let%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20part%2C%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20making%20this%20choice%20because%20other%20parents%20weren't%20afraid%20to%20parent%20him.%20It%20didn't%20actually%20feel%20like%20he%20was%20going%20out%20on%20his%20own.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20moving%20back%20to%20the%20US%2C%20now%20living%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20we've%20started%20letting%20our%20youngest%2C%20in%20second%20grade%2C%20walk%20to%20school%20on%20his%20own%20after%20several%20trial%20runs%20with%20us%20following%20close%20behind.%20He's%20the%20only%20one%20in%20his%20class%20who%20walks%20to%20school%20on%20his%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222bf44307-3d95-4a40-bec8-3d0d842bf396%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EChildcare%20is%20subsidized%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20childcare%20is%20subsidized%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20start%20my%20own%20circular%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhellojackalo.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echildren's%20clothing%20company%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20even%20while%20raising%20young%20children.%20It%20was%20absolutely%20amazing.%20There%20would%20have%20been%20no%20way%20I%20would%20have%20been%20able%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business%20while%20paying%20childcare%20fees%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20thing%20I%20really%20loved%20was%20that%20empty-nester%20grandparents%20could%20care%20for%20their%20own%20grandchildren%20and%20other%20people's%20children%2C%20and%20that%2C%20too%2C%20was%20subsidized.%20It%20gives%20grandparents%20a%20modest%20income%20and%20provides%20the%20younger%20generation%20with%20help%20to%20get%20back%20into%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b94827fb-7c6f-41e8-b323-dd3700fda208%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20learn%20how%20to%20read%20later%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20United%20States%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20to%20get%20kids%20ready%20by%20kindergarten.%20I%20know%20parents%20who%20freak%20out%20because%20their%20children%20haven't%20learned%20to%20read%20by%20age%204.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20were%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20they%20didn't%20really%20start%20reading%20until%207%20years%20old.%20They%20are%20just%20doing%20all%20the%20pre-reading%2C%20becoming%20curious.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20coming%20back%2C%20we%20stand%20out%20as%20a%20little%20weird%20after%20our%20time%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%20I%20really%20believe%20in%20the%20value%20of%20independence%20for%20kids.%20I%20have%20seen%20how%20much%20happier%20children%20are%20when%20they%20have%20independence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-netherlands-differences-in-parenting-according-to-american-mom-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715601722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e53f8b4abc992e8c83eab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-vs-netherlands-differences-in-parenting-according-to-american-mom-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mariann