ncourage%20revolutionary%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20would%20later%20write%20in%20his%20book%20%26quot%3BBehind%20the%20Cloud%3A%20The%20Untold%20Story%20of%20How%20Salesforce.com%20Went%20from%20Idea%20to%20Billion-dollar%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Revolutionized%20an%20Industry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJobs%20became%20one%20of%20Benioff's%20mentors.%20%26quot%3BThere%20would%20be%20no%20Salesforce.com%20without%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Benioff%20said%20in%202013%2C%20according%20to%20Entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBenioff%20graduated%20with%20a%20B.S.%20in%20Business%20Administration%20in%201986.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223116%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22marc%20benioff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d223f69a17d6c2ea0263292%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222337%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBenioff%20delivering%20the%20keynote%20address%20during%20commencement%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%20in%202015.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FNoah%20Berger%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUSC%20named%20him%20an%20honorary%20Doctor%20of%20Humane%20Letters%20in%202014.%20He%20now%20sits%20on%20the%20University's%20Board%20of%20Trustees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff%20planned%20to%20stay%20in%20programming%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20career%2C%20but%20a%20USC%20professor%20suggested%20he%20might%20have%20a%20mind%20for%20business.%20So%20he%20took%20a%20customer%20support%20role%20at%20high-flying%20database%20company%20Oracle%20right%20out%20of%20college%2C%20according%20to%20his%20%26quot%3BBehind%20the%20Cloud%26quot%3B%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBenioff%20rapidly%20rose%20up%20the%20ranks%20at%20Oracle%20after%20starting%20in%201986.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221771%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oracle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525800655f52b01b35b2f34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EB