01986%20to%201999.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Ellison's%20permission%2C%20Benioff%20took%20a%20sabbatical%20to%20travel%20the%20world.%20He%20spent%20part%20of%20that%20time%20studying%20meditation%20in%20Hawaii.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBenioff%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20for%20Salesforce%20while%20swimming%20with%20dolphins.%20He%20soon%20started%20working%20on%20the%20company%20with%20a%20few%20other%20Oracle%20veterans%2C%20Entrepreneur%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESalesforce%20was%20a%20revolutionary%20idea%20in%201999.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marc%20Benioff%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F51d1a3b3eab8eabc6a000013%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22359%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESalesforce%20took%20the%20tech%20industry%20by%20storm%20when%20it%20launched.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FJulie%20Bort%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20big%20idea%20behind%20Salesforce%20was%20that%20while%20most%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Oracle%20%E2%80%94%20sold%20enterprise%20software%20that%20companies%20had%20to%20install%20on%20their%20own%20servers%2C%20Salesforce%20could%20let%20people%20access%20business%20software%20from%20a%20web%20browser.%20For%20the%20late%20nineties%2C%20this%20was%20revolutionary%2C%20Benioff%20wrote%20in%20%26quot%3BBehind%20the%20Cloud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20first%2C%20Ellison%20was%20supportive%20of%20Benioff.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222135%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22larry%20ellison%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F545a87e66bb3f76c5c8b456d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221427%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllison%20and%20Benioff's%20relationship%20has%20fluctuated%20over%20the%20years.%3Cp%3EEzra%20Shaw%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F