3%25%20in%20the%20six%20months%20before%20that%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20drew%20its%20analysis%20from%20daily%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20Ukrainian%20Air%20Force%20Command%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20struggled%20to%20intercept%20Russia's%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20as%20it%20runs%20dangerously%20low%20on%20air%20defense%20systems%20and%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20cited%20by%20the%20Journal%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20shot%20down%20just%2010%25%20of%20Russian%20ballistic%20missiles%20and%20has%20failed%20to%20intercept%20any%20S-300%20and%20S-400%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Russia%20into%20Ukraine%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Russia%20has%20ramped%20up%20its%20drone%20and%20missile%20attacks%20by%20around%2045%25%20over%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported%2C%20citing%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20almost%20doubled%20the%20number%20of%20Shahed%20drones%20it%20has%20deployed%2C%20tripled%20the%20number%20of%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20doubled%20the%20number%20of%20hypersonic%20Kinzhal%20and%20Zircon%20missiles%20it%20has%20fired%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20preceding%20six%20months%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20gaps%20in%20the%20data%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20using%20it%20for%20propaganda%20purposes%2C%20an%20unnamed%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20an%20unnamed%20independent%20defense%20analyst%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20the%20statistics%20gave%20an%20overall%20accurate%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20picture%20that%20will%20be%20of%20concern%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20is%20waiting%20on%20significant%20resources%20from%20the%20US%20after%20Republicans%20in%20Congress%20finally%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-should-treat-latest-aid-like-the-last-war-experts-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eagreed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20%2461%20billion%20military%20aid%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20vote%20in%20Congress%2C%20the%20Pentagon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-aid-could-arrive-within-week-after-congress-greenlight-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20could%20rush%20vital%20air%20defense%20weapons%20and%20artillery%20shells%20to%20Ukraine%20within%20days%20of%20the%20military%20aid%20bill%20clearing%20the%20Senate%20and%20receiving%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20signature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-may-8-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eassessment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20The%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%2C%20Russia%20is%20exploiting%20Ukraine's%20weakened%20air%20defense%20systems%20before%20further%20supplies%20make%20it%20to%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Russia's%20large-scale%20bombardments%20have%20the%20potential%20to%20overwhelm%20Ukrainian%20defenses%20while%20also%20depleting%20ammunition%20supplies%2C%20making%20it%20sometimes%20impossible%20for%20air%20defense%20systems%20to%20reload%20fast%20enough%2C%20an%20unnamed%20UAF%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20unnamed%20European%20military%20intelligence%20official%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20the%20next%20two%20months%20or%20so%20will%20be%20key%20in%20determining%20whether%20Russian%20forces%20can%20be%20stopped%20before%20Western%20air%20defense%20systems%20reach%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-shot-down-just-30-percent-russia-missiles-april-report-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%