e-russian-law-that-has-georgians-out-on-the-streets-in-their-thousands-13135115%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-is-the-russian-law-that-has-georgians-out-on-the-streets-in-their-thousands-13135115%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwhat-is-the-russian-law-that-has-georgians-out-on-the-streets-in-their-thousands-13135115%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBJP%20Washed%20Temple%20After%20My%20Visit%26quot%3B%3A%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Reminder%20To%20Kannauj%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20today%20from%20the%20Kannauj%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20says%20he%20is%20secure%20in%20the%20support%20of%20Dalits%2C%20that%20came%20to%20the%20party%20when%20it%20had%20tied%20up%20with%20Mayawati's%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20in%202019.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20implied%2C%20despises%20the%20so-called%20lower%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20to%20a%20temple%2C%20the%20BJP%20got%20it%20washed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP%20workers'%20purification%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Gauri%20Shankar%20Mahadev%20Mandir%20of%20Kannauj%20after%20his%20visit.%20A%20video%20of%20the%20purification%20ceremony%20was%20widely%20circulated%20in%20social%20media%20and%20the%20incident%20had%20provided%20boost%20to%20the%20SP%20efforts%20to%20weave%20a%20rainbow%20support%20group%20of%20voters%20at%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20fight%20is%20big.%20Today%2C%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%20which%20taught%20us%20how%20to%20live...%20They%20will%20do%20so%20if%20they%20get%20400%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20underscoring%20what%20has%20become%20the%20Opposition's%20biggest%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Yadav%20has%20returned%20to%20Kannauj%20to%20reclaim%20an%20old%20family%20bastion%20--%20his%20father%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20nurtured%20the%20constituency%20for%20years.%20But%20the%20seat%20went%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202019%20and%20sitting%20MP%20and%20perfume%20trader%20Subrat%20Pathak%20is%20out%20to%20defend%20it.%20The%20battle%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20centrepiece%20of%20today's%20election%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20voting%20is%20being%20held%20on%20nine%20other%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20will%20be%20triangular%20with%20the%20BSP%20fielding%20Imran%20Bin%20Zafar.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BKannauj%20parliamentary%20constituency%20has%20taught%20me%20the%20ABCD%20of%20politics...%20I%20grew%20in%20politics%20in%20Kannauj%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%20today%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20political%20debut%20from%20the%20seat%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20for%20Kannauj%20will%20be%20the%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20battle%20for%20the%20SP%20chief%20in%20a%20long%20time.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20had%20resigned%20his%20Azamgarh%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20and%20retained%20the%20assembly%20seat%20from%20Karhal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pathak%20has%20been%20a%20repeat%20contestant%20from%20the%20seat%20since%202009%20and%20ended%20the%20SP's%2035-year%20dream%20run%20at%20the%20constituency%20after%20a%20decade%20in%202019.%20His%20opponent%20was%20Dimple%20Yadav%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20SP%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReminding%20voters%20of%20the%20old%20times%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20of%20Kannauj%20know%20how%20much%20development%20took%20place%20when%20Samajwadi%20Party%20was%20in%20power%20and%20why%20development%20is%20not%20happening%20here%20today%E2%80%A6%20We%20gave%20world%20class%20infrastructure%20to%20Kannauj%2C%20built%20the%20world's%20best%20roads...%20built%20a%20market%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715598360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fo1iv3lfo_akhilesh-yadav_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http