rticles%2Fcrgyymn8y3ro.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kapil%20CONFIRMS%20Ed%20Sheeran's%20appearance%20on%20show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715594364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110082241%2Cimgsize-28856.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkapil-sharma-announces-ed-sheerans-appearance-on-the-great-indian-kapil-show-episode-airing-on-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F110082241.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F110082241.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EEd%20Sheeran's%20upcoming%20appearance%20on%20The%20Great%20Indian%20Kapil%20Show%20has%20fans%20buzzing%20with%20excitement.%20The%20news%20broke%20after%20a%20special%20promo%20aired%20following%20the%20latest%20episode%20featuring%20the%20cast%20of%20'Heeramandi'.%20Scheduled%20for%20May%2018%2C%20the%20episode%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20delightful%20treat%20for%20viewers.%20In%20the%20promo%2C%20Ed%20Sheeran%20is%20seen%20thoroughly%20enjoying%20himself%2C%20even%20bringing%20his%20guitar%20along%20for%20the%20ride.%20Kapil%20Sharma%2C%20known%20for%20his%20wit%20and%20humor%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20switching%20gears%20for%20this%20episode%2C%20primarily%20conversing%20in%20English%20with%20Ed.%20Kapil%20proudly%20mentioned%20Ed's%20multiple%20visits%20to%20India%20before%20welcoming%20him%20on%20the%20show%2C%20teasing%20that%20the%20international%20star%20came%20just%20to%20meet%20him.%20However%2C%20Ed%20humbly%20clarified%20in%20Hindi%20that%20he%20was%20in%20India%20for%20a%20concert.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkapil-sharma-announces-ed-sheerans-appearance-on-the-great-indian-kapil-show-episode-airing-on-this-date%2Farticleshow%2F110082241.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Zerodha's%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20Opens%20Up%20Why%20He%20Doesn't%20Have%20Children%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20his%20podcast%2C%20WTF%2C%20Zerodha%20co-founder%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20discussed%20his%20views%20on%20parenthood.%20He%20mentioned%20that%20the%20traditional%20idea%20of%20having%20children%20to%20carry%20on%20a%20legacy%20doesn't%20resonate%20with%20him.%20He%20prioritises%20his%20current%20pursuits%20and%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20dedicate%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20his%20life%20to%20raising%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20also%20partly%20why%20I%20don't%20have%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamath%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20ruin%2018-20%20years%20of%20my%20life%20babysitting%20this%20child%20and%20then%20if%20luck%20serves%20me%20right%2C%20the%20reverse%20will%20happen%20at%20some%20point.%20What%20if%20he%20says%20'scr**%20you'%20at%2018%20and%20leave%20anyway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20topic%20of%20legacy%20came%20up%2C%20the%2037-year-old%20entrepreneur%20revealed%20he%20doesn't%20subscribe%20to%20the%20traditional%20idea%20of%20leaving%20one%20behind.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20all%20feel%20that%20we%20are%20more%20important%20than%20we%20are...%20you%20are%20born%20and%20you%20die%20like%20every%20other%20animal%20on%20the%20planet%20and%20then%20you%20are%20gone%20and%20nobody%20remembers%20anybody%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Kamath%20further%20explained%20that%20having%20children%20solely%20to%20ensure%20he's%20remembered%20after%20death%20doesn't%20align%20with%20his%20values.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20point%20in%20being%20remembered%20(after%20death)%3F%20I%20feel%20like%20you%20should%20come%2C%20you%20should%20live%20well%2C%20you%20should%20be%20nice%20to%20the%20people%20you%20meet%20in%20your%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemonstrating%20his%20dedication%20to%20social%20good%2C%20Zerodha%20co-founder%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20became%20the%20youngest%20Indian%20signatory%20to%20The%20Giving%20Pledge%20last%20year.%20This%20prestigious%20initiative%20unites%20philanthropists%20who%20commit%20a%20majority%20of%20their%20wealth%20to%20charitable%20causes.%20Mr%20Kamath%20credits%20fellow%20Bengaluru%20entrepreneurs%20and%20pledgers%2C%20Infosys%20co-founder%20Nandan%20Nilekani%2C%20Biocon%20founder%20Kiran%20Mazumdar-Shaw%2C%20and%20Wipro%20founder%20Azim%20Premji%2C%20as%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20for%20his%20own%20philanthropic%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20there%20are%20four%20people%20in%20India%20who%20have%20signed%20The%20Giving%20Pledge%20--%20the%20other%20three%20happen%20to%20be%20really%20good%20friends%20of%20mine.%20And%20Bangaloreans%20will%20resonate%20with%20this%20--%20all%20of%20them%20are%20from%20Bangalore.%20All%20four%20of%20us%20are%20friends.%20Me%20and%20Kiran%20live%20in%20the%20same%20apartment%E2%80%A6%20we%20all%20tend%20to%20meet%20once%20in%20a%20month%20for%20dinner%20or%20travel%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Kamath%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20dedicate%20a%20majority%20of%20his%20wealth%20to%20philanthropy%2C%20Zerodha%20co-founder%20Nikhil%20Kamath%20pointed%20to%20the%20influence%20of%20his%20fellow%20philanthropists%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20are%20also%20signatories%20of%20The%20Giving%20Pledge.%20Witnessing%20their%20dedication%20to%20social%20good%20inspired%20him%20to%20maximize%20the%20positive%20impact%20of%20his%20own%20wealth.%20%C2%A0He%20expressed%20a%20preference%20for%20directing%20his%20resources%20towards%20causes%20he%20values%20rather%20than%20accumulating%20wealth%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20everybody%20should%20realise%20the%20importance%20and%20understand%20the%20concept%20of%20mortality...%20I%20am%2037%20and%20if%20the%20average%20lifespan%20of%20an%20Indian%20is%2072%20years%20old%2C%20I%20have%2035%20years%20left.%20There%20is%20no%20value%20in%20leaving%20money%20in%20the%20banks%E2%80%A6%20so%20I%20would%20rather%20give%20it%20to%20things%20I%20believe%20in.%20So%20rather%20than%20leaving%20the%20money%20I%20have%20earned%20in%20the%20last%2020%20years%20and%20what%20I%20would%20earn%20in%20the%20next%2020%20years%20to%20a%20bank%20or%20institution%20like%20that%E2%80%A6%20I%20would%20rather%20make%20the%20most%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kamath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715593680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Faqq91reo_nikhil-kamath_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nikhil-kamath-opens-up-why-he-doesnt-have-children-going-to-ruin-5652988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Kamath%20prioritises%20his%20current%20pursuits%20and%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20dedicate%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20his%20life%20to%20raising%20a%20child.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nikhil-kamath-opens-up-why-he-doesnt-have-children-going-to-ruin-5652988%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nikhil-kamath-opens-up-why-he-doesnt-have-children-going-to-ruin-5652988%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fzerodhas-nikhil-kamath-opens-up-why-he-doesnt-have-children-going-to-ruin-5652988%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20Ji%20Chang%20Wook's%20Jakarta%20fan%20event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715593471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110081492%2Cimgsize-54924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-seri