0his%20former%20economy%20aide%20and%20First%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Andrey%20Belousov%2C%2065%2C%20to%20be%20Russia's%20new%20defense%20minister.%20Belousov%20replaces%20Sergei%20Shoigu%2C%2068%2C%20who'd%20been%20defense%20minister%20since%202012%20and%20is%20being%20transferred%20to%20a%20new%20role%20as%20secretary%20of%20Russia's%20security%20council.%20Nikolai%20Patrushev%2C%20a%20longtime%20ally%20of%20Putin%20who%20had%20held%20that%20post%2C%20was%20dismissed%20and%20is%20due%20to%20take%20another%2C%20unspecified%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20of%20Belousov%2C%20who%20has%20long%20advocated%20greater%20state%20control%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20about%20military%20leadership%2C%26quot%3B%20Tatyana%20Stanovaya%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20political%20consultancy%20R.Politik%2C%20said%20on%20Telegram.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20about%20'Gosplan'%20in%20the%20military-industrial%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Soviet-era%20state-planning%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20came%20to%20his%20decision%20to%20appoint%20Belousov%20in%20part%20because%20he's%20a%20student%20of%20history%20and%20had%20in%20mind%20the%20example%20of%20former%20US%20Defense%20Secretary%20Robert%20McNamara%2C%20according%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20government%20deliberations%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20an%20internal%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20defense%20secretary%20under%20Presidents%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20and%20Lyndon%20B.%20Johnson%20in%20the%201960s%20during%20the%20Vietnam%20War%2C%20McNamara%20overhauled%20military%20procurement%20to%20improve%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin's%20ouster%20of%20Shoigu%2C%20one%20of%20his%20closest%20allies%2C%20may%20reflect%20frustration%20at%20the%20failure%20to%20defeat%20Ukraine%20in%20a%20war%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20last%20for%20days%20and%20is%20now%20in%20its%20third%20year%20with%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Russian%20troops%20killed%20or%20wounded.%20The%20defense%20minister%20was%20the%20target%20of%20last%20year's%20aborted%20mutiny%20by%20Wagner%20mercenary%20leader%20Yevgeny%20Prighozin%2C%20who%20accused%20him%20of%20repeated%20failures%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20troops%20are%20advancing%20in%20Ukraine's%20northeastern%20Kharkiv%20region%2C%20in%20a%20new%20offensive.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskiy%20said%20late%20Sunday%20that%20defense%20forces%20were%20holding%20their%20positions%20in%20fierce%20battles%2C%20calling%20the%20situation%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin's%20determined%20to%20achieve%20a%20minimum%20war%20goal%20of%20seizing%20full%20control%20of%20eastern%20Ukraine's%20Donbas%20region%2C%20following%20the%20years-long%20conflict%20stoked%20by%20Moscow%20that%20provided%20his%20justification%20for%20the%20February%202022%20invasion%2C%20said%20two%20people%20familiar%20with%20Russia's%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20overhaul%20takes%20place%20as%20Putin%20prepares%20to%20travel%20to%20China%20this%20week%20for%20talks%20with%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20The%20visit%20underscores%20the%20importance%20for%20the%20Kremlin%20leader%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bno%20limits%26quot%3B%20friendship%20with%20Beijing%20that%20has%20enabled%20Moscow%20to%20weather%20unprecedented%20sanctions%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20to%20try%20to%20wreck%20Russia's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Shoigu%2C%20Belousov%20arrives%20at%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20with%20no%20military%20background.%20With%20Ukraine%20starting%20to%20receive%20tens%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20new%20military%20aid%20from%20its%20US%20and%20European%20allies%2C%20Russia%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20maximizing%20the%20impact%20of%20its%20own%20defense%20spending%2C%20which%20is%20surging%20to%20historically%20high%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9g4fgg68_putin-russia-war_625x300_13_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20spending%20on%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%20and%20Russia's%20security%20sector%20is%20approaching%206.7%25%20of%20gross%20domestic%20product%2C%20nearing%20levels%20reached%20by%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Cold%20War%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20Kremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20said%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Interfax%20news%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20spending%20levels%20aren't%20yet%20%26quot%3Bcritical%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20chose%20Belousov%20because%20of%20the%20need%20for%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20competitiveness%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Defense%20Ministry%2C%20Peskov%20said%2C%20Interfax%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBelousov's%20appointment%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20Russian%20economy%20is%20being%20transformed%20into%20a%20war%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Andrei%20Kolesnikov%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace%20in%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shuffle%20is%20the%20most%20far-reaching%20shakeup%20since%202020%2C%20when%20Putin%20named%20Mikhail%20Mishustin%20to%20replace%20Dmitry%20Medvedev%20as%20prime%20minister.%20Months%20later%2C%20Putin%20overhauled%20the%20Constitution%20to%20allow%20him%20two%20more%20mandates%2C%20which%20means%20he%20could%20rule%20to%202036%2C%20when%20he'll%20be%2083.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMishustin%20was%20reappointed%20last%20week%20to%20continue%20as%20prime%20minister.%20Medvedev%20has%20been%20deputy%20head%20of%20the%20security%20council%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20watchers%20will%20be%20keenly%20monitoring%20the%20fate%20of%20Patrushev%2C%2072%2C%20who'd%20been%20the%20hawkish%20head%20of%20the%20security%20council%20since%202008%20and%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20The%20former%20KGB%20agent%20succeeded%20Putin%20as%20Federal%20Security%20Service%20chief%20when%20the%20latter%20was%20named%20Russia's%20prime%20minister%20in%201999%20and%20Patrushev%20continued%20in%20that%20post%20to%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20son%2C%20Dmitry%20Patrushev%2C%20was%20promoted%20to%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20overseeing%20Russia's%20agriculture%20industry%20in%20the%20government%20shuffle%20that%20has%20followed%20Putin's%20inauguration%20last%20week%20for%20a%20fifth%20term%20as%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20named%20Sergei%20Lavrov%2C%2074%2C%20to%20continue%20as%20foreign%20minister%2C%20extending%20his%20tenure%20in%20the%20post%20that%20he's%20held%20for%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20also%20proposed%20retaining%20Alexander%20Bortnikov%20as%20head%20of%20the%20FSB%20security%20service%20and%20Sergei%20Naryshkin%20as%20director%20of%20Russia's%20foreign%20intelligence%20service.%20Viktor%20Zolotov%20would%20also%20continue%20as%20head%20of%20Russia's%20national%20guard%20in%20the%20list%20of%20appointments%20sent%20to%20the%20Federation%20Council%2C%20Russia's%20upper%20house%20of%20parliament%2C%20for%20confirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20the%20council%20will%20meet%20on%20Monday%20to%20discuss%20the%20president's%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715588760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhg39e7do_putin_625x300_13_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fputin-turns-to-a-technocrat-to-crank-up-russia-war-machine-5652380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20surprise%20late-night%20shuffle%20of%20his%20defense%20and%20security%20team%20signals%20his%20determination%20to%20mobilize%20Russia's%20war%20economy%20for%20a%20long%