n%20is%20still%20going%20on.%20He%20may%20get%20acquitted.%20What%20will%20you%20do%20then%3F%20Come%20after%20he%20is%20convicted%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20Rajendra%20Menon%20said%20then%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejiwal-leaves-jail-after-50-days-election-gamechanger-says-aap-5633876%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKejriwal%20Leaves%20Jail%20After%2050%20Days%2C%20Says%20%26quot%3BNeed%20To%20Fight%20Dictatorship%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20March%2021%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20that%20roiled%20the%20AAP%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%20The%20arresting%20agency%20-%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20-%20has%20claimed%20the%20(now%20scrapped)%20policy%20allowed%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20receive%20kickbacks%20for%20license%20allotment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20kickbacks%20amounted%20to%20Rs%20100%20crores%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20alleged%2C%20and%20was%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20AAP's%20election%20campaigns%20in%20Goa%20and%20Punjab.%20The%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20denied%20all%20charges%20and%20have%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20making%20false%20accusations%20to%20discredit%20the%20party%20and%20its%20leaders%20before%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20-%20who%20refused%20to%20step%20down%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20after%20his%20arrest%2C%20pointing%20out%20he%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20convicted%20and%20even%20passing%20a%20few%20orders%20to%20his%20government%20-%20was%20released%20on%20interim%20bail%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20he%20had%20to%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%20before%20Delhi's%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20position%20as%20an%20elected%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20these%20are%20extraordinary%20circumstances%2C%20and%20he%20is%20not%20a%20habitual%20offender.%20This%20is%20a%20question%20of%20public%20interest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-fundamental-right-to-campaign-probe-agency-opposes-bail-for-arvind-kejriwal-5624891%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNo%20Fundamental%20Right%20To%20Campaign%26quot%3B%3A%20ED%20Opposes%20Bail%20For%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20opposed%20bail%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20declaring%20no%20politician%20could%20claim%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20status%26quot%3B%20higher%20than%20that%20of%20a%20citizen%2C%20and%20is%20as%20liable%20to%20be%20arrested%20for%20committing%20offences%20as%20any%20other%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20out%20on%20interim%20bail%20till%20June%201%3B%20he%20must%20surrender%20to%20prison%20authorities%20by%20June%202.%20He%20had%20sought%20an%20extended%20bail%20-%20till%20after%20the%20results%20are%20declared%20on%20June%204%20-%20but%20the%20court%20turned%20him%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715588100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4i6uabig_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_12_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-bail-supreme-court-no-legal-merit-supreme-court-junks-another-plea-to-sack-arvind-kejriwal-5651938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20snubbed%20a%20petition%20seeking%20the%20removal%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20