%20That%20longing%20brought%20us%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Kabir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20shares%20how%20in%20the%20small%20hill%20station%2C%20with%20fewer%20work%20opportunities%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20of%20the%20talent%20moves%20out.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20outside%20is%20a%20common%20trend%20and%20the%20people%20from%20our%20generation%20never%20really%20come%20back%20home.%20Kabir%20and%20I%20always%20had%20this%20idea%2C%20that%20we%20would%20come%20home%20and%20do%20something%20that%20would%20employ%20more%20local%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kabir%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20hospitality%20industry%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344999%2Fhomestay-in-panchgani-roadtrip-from-mumbai-sustainable-organic-food-solar-panel-long-weekend-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarting%20a%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Eseemed%20like%20a%20natural%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20959px)%20100vw%2C%20959px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kabir%20and%20Ahana%20moved%20back%20to%20Kalimpong%20to%20build%20homestay%20of%20their%20dreams.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085.jpg%20959w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-1-1-1-1-1715264085-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FPaddy-plantation-farm-activities-1-