%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-1-1715240394-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPathshala%20started%20as%20a%20mobile%20teaching%20initiative%20before%20Juin%20converted%20it%20into%20a%20residential%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20to%20their%20efforts%20was%20good%2C%20so%20the%20group%20divided%20their%20efforts%20and%20started%20to%20teach%20in%20three%20different%20locations%20in%20Vadodara.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20some%20months%2C%20from%20a%20dozen%20kids%2C%20we%20went%20to%20teaching%20hundreds.%20But%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20every%20six%20months%2C%20these%20workers%20would%20move%20and%20hence%20the%20kids%20would%20be%20left%20with%20no%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20mothers%20who%20requested%20Juin%20to%20take%20her%20child%20under%20her%20wing%20and%20provide%20education%20as%20they%20were%20to%20migrate%20once%20more.%20Inspired%20by%20it%2C%20in%202014%2C%20Juin%20decided%20to%20resign%20from%20her%20job%20and%20dedicate%20herself%20to%20assisting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F100208%2Fsnehlata-hooda-teaching-underprivileged-children-in-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderprivileged%20children.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20hostel%20