damentally%20a%20value-based%20institution%2C%20dedicated%20to%20nurturing%20children%E2%80%99s%20happiness%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESejal%20Verma%20(21)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20few%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20their%20education%20and%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20hostel%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20currently%20working%20part-time%20and%20earning%20enough%20to%20support%20myself.%20I%E2%80%99m%20also%20pursuing%20a%20course%20at%20ITI%20Vadodara.%20However%2C%20none%20of%20this%20would%20have%20been%20possible%20if%20I%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20gained%20admission%20to%20Pathshala%20on%20time.%20I%20had%20passed%20my%20Class%208%20exam%20from%20a%20Government%20school%20but%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20read%20the%20alphabet!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20many%20ways%2C%20I%20restarted%20my%20education%20at%20Pathshala.%20Once%20I%20completed%20my%20boards%2C%20they%20helped%20me%20get%20admitted%20into%20ITI%2C%20and%20I%20still%20visit%20the%20hostel.%20It%20feels%20like%20home%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20visiting%20the%20children%20on%20various%20occasions%20like%20festivals%20and%20school%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20rely%20on%20the%20kindness%20of%20humans%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20only%20seven%20children%20with%20us%20when%20we%20started%2C%20and%20now%2C%20we%20have%20grown%20to%2097%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Juin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20when%20she%20observed%20the%20number%20of%20children%20growing%20in%20the%20hostel%20that%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20a%20bigger%20place.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20had%20around%20one%20and%20a%20half%20lakh%20rupees%20on%20hand%20and%20were%20searching%20for%20funds.%20But%20our%20motivation%20to%20help%20these%20kids%20kept%20us%20going.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20encountered%20generous%20individuals%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20support%20us.