g%20millets%20was%20one%20part%20of%20the%20vision%2C%20the%20other%20part%20was%20drawn%20from%20their%20experiences.%20They%20noticed%20a%20shift%20towards%20healthy%2C%20vegan%20food%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20dietary%20requirements%20were%20changing.%20There%20was%20an%20increasing%20demand%20for%20vegan%2C%20non-dairy%20alternatives%2C%20as%20more%20people%20are%20getting%20lactose%20intolerant.%20In%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20people%20were%20asking%20for%20almond%20and%20oats%20milk%2C%20which%20made%20us%20wonder%20about%20an%20Indian%2C%20vegan%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prabu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20years%20after%20starting%20Siri%20Millets%2C%20they%20launched%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eladdoos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cookies%2C%20vermicelli%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Erava.%3C%2Fem%3E%20They%20piloted%20these%20value-added%20products%20in%20Telangana%20and%20Gujarat%20by%20providing%20them%20to%20students%20in%20government%20schools%20for%2045%20days%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20founders%20conduct%20awareness%20programs%20in%20schools%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691-300x212.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-10-at-10.50.45-min-1715318691-500x353.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%