nths%20and%20then%20launched%20their%20first%20%E2%80%98Siri%20%E2%80%93%20House%20of%20Vegan%20Ice%20Creams%E2%80%99%20store%20in%20Trichy%20in%202020.%20The%20flavours%20they%20offer%20range%20from%20vanilla%2C%20chocolate%2C%20mango%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20and%20jamun%2C%20to%20red%20guava%2C%20dates%2C%20banana%2C%20musk%20melon%2C%20strawberry%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnlike%20coconut%20milk%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20vegan%20ice%20creams%2C%20millet%20milk%20is%20subtle%20and%20does%20not%20dominate%20other%20flavours.%20We%20use%20different%20sweeteners%20in%20different%20ice%20creams%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20fruits%20being%20used.%20For%20example%2C%20jaggery%20works%20well%20with%20some%20fruits%2C%20while%20palm%20sugar%20works%20better%20with%20some.%20It%20also%20varies%20depending%20on%20the%20millet%20being%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Prabu%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20also%20sell%20shakes%2C%20waffles%2C%20brownies%2C%20and%20other%20products%20in%20their%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20scoop%20of%20ice%20cream%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2030%2C%20and%20a%20one-litre%20pack%20is%20sold%20for%20Rs%20800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20factory%20in%20Trichy%20has%20a%2010%2C000-litre%20capacity%20per%20shift.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fsiri-factory-1715318645-76