in%20washed%20away%20entire%20houses.%20Wohab%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Howrah%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalls%20the%20harrowing%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20people%20and%20their%20cattle%20drowning%20in%20the%20water.%20All%20around%2C%20flood%20victims%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20other%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20schools%2C%20and%20even%20climbing%20up%20trees%20to%20avoid%20drowning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20week%2C%20much%20less%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20would%20bring.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20chaos%20that%20Wohab%20watched%20as%20a%20man%2C%20who%20seemed%20like%20a%20foreigner%2C%20was%20rowing%20his%20boat%20through%20the%20floodwater%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329667%2Fpalghar-kiran-kamdar-free-homemade-khichdi-for-patients-hospital-parkinson-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20food%20packets%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20people.%20This%20attracted%20the%20lawyer%20who%20was%20working%20as%20secretary%20to%20a%20village-level%20governing%20body%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20all%20essential%20medical%20equipment%20and%20medicines%20needed%20to%20help%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo