3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20something%20about%20the%20land%20which%20made%20me%20want%20to%20conserve%20biodiversity.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20place%2C%20I%20could%20envision%20a%20spot%20much%20more%20than%20a%20barren%20plot.%20I%20immediately%20started%20to%20draw%20a%20plan%20with%20my%20team%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%202023%2C%2011%20months%20later%2C%20Vikas%20was%20able%20to%20build%20Rapdi%20Ecotourism%20Centre%20along%20with%20his%20team.%20%E2%80%9COn%20its%20opening%20day%2C%20we%20had%20about%201%2C100%20people%20swarming%20the%20place%2C%20which%20is%20a%20lot%20for%20a%20place%20like%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20muses%20Vikas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20attempting%20to%20save%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20place%20was%20a%20key%20factor%2C%20there%20was%20another%20reason%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20place%20%E2%80%94%20spreading%20awareness%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282775%2Frobinson-crusoe-worlds-remotest-island-to-document-conserve-biodiversity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20tourism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20ravine%20experience%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20a%20short%20drive%20away%20from%20Shikohabad%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Firozabad%2C%20the%20place%20is%20home%20to%20hundreds%20of%20trees%2C%20wooden%20huts%2C%20boats%20and%20a%20lot%20more%20and%20was%20%E2%80%9Ctaken%20up%20to%20create%20the%20first%20ecotourism%20facility%20in%20the%20district.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20first%20posted%20in%20the%20area%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20did%20not%20have%20any%20ecotourism%20place.%20The%20locals%20were%20not%20very%20active%20in%20natural%20conservation%20either%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20a