t%20have%20enough%20money%20to%20buy%20her%20bangles.%20In%202004%2C%20my%20mother%20started%20taking%20stitching%20classes%20and%20selling%20suits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%202011%2C%20our%20situation%20improved%20when%20my%20father%20joined%20the%20business%20after%20quitting%20his%20retail%20outlet%20job.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkush%20says%20his%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing%20legacy.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%E2%80%99s%20situation%20has%20not%20only%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20humble%20and%20grounded%20but%20also%20about%20running%20a%20business.%20Our%20everyday%20conversation%20would%20be%20on%20sales%20and%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ankush%20%E2%80%94%20a%20computer%20science%20graduate%20by%20education%20%E2%80%94%20took%20up%20a%20sales%20and%20marketing%20job%20in%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20company.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20this%20work%2C%20I%20met%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276751%2Fsuta-sarees-brand-helps-weavers-artisans-earn-sujata-taniya-biswas%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaree%20manufacturer%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20was%20counting%20profits%20after%20selling%20100%20sarees%20for%20Rs%20300%20each.%20After%20speaking%20with%20him%2C%20I%20understood%20that%20while%20manufacturers%20make%20a%20saree%20for%20Rs%20300%2C%20they%20are%20sold%20for%20Rs%201%2C000%20in%20the%20same%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-2-1714728986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22To%20sustain%20this%20large%20family%2C%20Ankush%20says%20his%20grandfather%20would%20peddle%20clothes%20door%20to%20door.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%