ailers%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20there%20is%20not%20one%20but%20many%20middlemen%20in%20the%20saree%20industry.%20Manufacturers%20deal%20with%20distributors%20and%20work%20on%20credit%20for%20one%20month.%20That%20means%20they%20will%20get%20payments%20after%20this%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20aimed%20to%20address%20these%20challenges%20with%20my%20startup.%20My%20solution%3F%20Once%20orders%20start%20rolling%20in%2C%20we%20commit%20to%20paying%20manufacturers%20promptly.%20My%20idea%20was%20that%20by%20opting%20for%20immediate%20payment%20instead%20of%20credit%2C%20they%20could%20enjoy%20a%20steady%20daily%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20understanding%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fsari-history-celebration-of-culture-on-republic-day-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaree%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ankush%20finally%20quit%20his%20high-paying%20job%20in%202021%20and%20launched%20Deeva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20a%20small%20village%20to%20Shark%20Tank%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20Deeva%2C%20Ankush%20exhausted%20all%20his%20savings%20of%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20and%20an%20additional%20Rs%203%20lakh%20financial%20support%20from%20his%20father.%20Much%20against%20his%20hopes%2C%20he%20experienced%20extreme%20losses.%20Amid%20societal%20pressure%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20where%20he%20pursued%20his%20higher%20education%20%E2%80%94%20to%20escape%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ankush%20says%20his%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing%20legacy.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FAnkush-3-1714729022-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348902%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnkush%20says%20his%20success%20is%20rooted%20in%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20clothing%20legacy.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20each%20other%20in%20a%20village.%20When%20villagers%20saw%20me%20struggle%20for%20my%20startup%2C%20they%20started%20throwing%20tantrums%20at%20my%20decision%20to%20quit%20a%20high-paying%20city%20job%20to%20run%20a%20saree%20shop.%20My%20family%20also%20kept%20asking%20me%20about%20my%20daily%20progress.%20I%20had%20no%20answers%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Chennai%20was%20a%20challenging%20chapter%20of%20his%20life.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20surviving%20on%20loans%20from%20friends.%20I%20was%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20rent%20and%20survived%20on%20one%20meal%20a%20day%20to%20save%20money.%20There%20were%20days%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20quit%3B%20I%20wanted%20to%20cry%20and%20go%20back%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ankush%20remembered%20all%20the%20promises%20of%20an%20opulent%20life%20that%20he%20made%20to%20his%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20find%20ways%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20a%20mobile%20app%2C%20Ankush%20designed%20a%20website%20for